Sogou,is,a,Chinese,search,engine,with,an,index,of,billion,web,pages,It,can,be,used,to,search,text,images,music,and,maps,The,Sogou,Search,Marketing,API,is,a,suite,of,services,that,let,developers,interact,with,the,Sogou,servers,programmatically,Developers,can,use,the,API,to,build,applications,that,manager,their,online,marketing,accounts,Users,must,register,for,the,service,and,approval,is,based,on,meeting,outlined,qualifications,The,API,uses,SOAP,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML